{
  "stem": "24462.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So this was the bright side of the life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I supplied the information to the Frenchman, whatever I could get from newspapers, or from radio, or from the BBC.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We were listening to the BBC, but not very often at the beginning.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "At the later stage, very often.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And almost-- and one day, we were listening to the BBC with the retreating German soldiers together.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But this is stages, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The life of the Poles was rather good.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Because they had-- some of the Poles have rented few flats in an apartment house, three or four flats.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And from-- in each flat they had two or three people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So the concentration was that nine or 10 people were living almost in the same place.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So we were meeting-- this was-- this place was called-- this was a hostel, kind of hostel, called [?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Wintergarten. ?] I don't have the translation, [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Wintergarten. ?] And this [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Wintergarten, ?] we met in the evenings, Sundays, holidays.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I have got pictures from the [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Wintergarten. ?] Some of them played accordion.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Some of them played-- the Poles played violin.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "One was playing flute.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I think this is the lot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But this was a lot-- a lot of music.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, we needed the girls to dance and to entertain.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Who was the provider?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was the provider.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because I met the Russian girls who came to a linen factory.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was already in '43.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They brought some 50 or 60 girls, Russian girls, to work in a linen factory.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What is a linen factory?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They-- they-- they were working on flax and linen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Whatever the-- I think the end product was some textiles.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the girls were free to leave, to-- to go on Sunday.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
